<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Kumsawt Pielgal Ah</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka lenna gamgaw taihsan in,
 Van Jerusalem thak nuom ah;
 Aw bangtikleh thuong ka tung dem ?
 Na kumsawt Pielgal gamah,

[V2]
 Aw ka ngai gibang khen lohna gam nuomah,
 Hinna tui a luong!
 Hukdam chate'n a dawn ui,
 Kumkhuo hinna chang ui.

[V3]
 2. Belam No lenna mun lopi.
 Ngaiin ni chengin ka galdawt;
 Aw thagau thiengtho hung lengin,
 Na gam nuom thuong ei tunin.

[V4]
 3. Dawngkawt gi hawih chu ahawng ui,
 A gi hawih in ka lung ei len;
 Mi thiengthote tuollenna ah,
 Aw keile len ka nuom hi.

[V5]
 4. Zie mun a chun ka Lal deihum,
 A mel nisa vanglai bangin;
 A vak haw chu a zam vel-a,
 Kumkhuo a damna dingin.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>297</hymn_number>
<author>Runchawng</author>
</song>